uch as EMQ and SNIP.', 'Experiment 3: Analyze the effect of curvature information on the quantization process, including the impact on accuracy and computational cost.'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['The proposed method may require significant computational resources for curvature analysis.', 'The method may not be effective for all types of deep learning models or tasks.', 'The choice of curvature metric and threshold may require careful tuning.']}
