ks'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ["SQR's performance may be sensitive to the choice of covariance estimation method and spectral decay rate", 'The approach may not generalize well to extremely low-latency or high-precision settings', "SQR's training-free nature may limit its ability to adapt to complex or dynamic input distributions"]}
