* Quantifying representations by their description length (MDL), entropy, and mutual information with the task
* Exploring the connection between compressibility and the information bottleneck

The proposal will be formulated as a simple and elegant question, observation, or hypothesis, and will clearly distinguish from existing literature. The experiments will be designed to be simple and feasible, with a focus on testing the hypothesis and evaluating the proposal using metrics such as distortion-rate frontiers and code efficiency relative to entropy.
