After conducting this search, I will analyze the results to identify areas where my preferences for hardware-first systems research, kernel-level throughput engineering, and empirical evaluation can lead to innovative contributions. This might involve exploring new techniques for optimizing fused CUDA/Triton kernels, memory-bandwidth utilization, or tensor-core occupancy, with a focus on achieving measurable, reproducible speedups on real hardware. 

