 compression algorithms that optimize the rate-distortion trade-off'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['The complexity of the rate-distortion framework may limit its applicability to very large models', 'The choice of distortion measure may affect the results and require careful consideration', 'The development of new compression algorithms may require significant computational resources and expertise']}
