istortion framework for neural network compression', 'Analyze the rate-distortion tradeoff in neural networks and identify the most compressible parts of the network', 'Develop new algorithms and techniques for compression and quantization based on the rate-distortion framework', 'Evaluate the performance of the proposed compression methods on a range of benchmark datasets and tasks'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['The development of a rate-distortion framework for neural network compression may be challenging due to the complexity of neural networks and the lack of a clear understanding of the rate-distortion tradeoff in these systems', 'The proposed compression methods may not achieve the expected compression ratios or may result in significant degradation in performance', 'The evaluation of the proposed methods may be limited by the availability of suitable benchmark datasets and tasks']}
